Troubleshooting Steps
Check disk space (df -h)
Checking prcessing (top, free ,lsmem , /proc/meminfo ,vmstat, lscpu)
check disk issues (iostat -y 5 ,lsof)
check networking (tcpdump -i <interface name> ,lsof -i -P -n | grep -i listen)
uptime
check logs 
check hardware status by loggin to console
other tools (htop , iotop)
